Volume-regulated anion channel subunit LRRC8A

6djb E 57 E 295

A redox-regulated disulphide may form within Volume-regulated anion channel subunit LRRC8A at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.
